Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:04.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,豐久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:05.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:07.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,伯父 請撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:11.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:17.56,Drifters Top,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(314.4,175.2)\fad(420,500)}西軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:17.56,Drifters Top,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(172.8,451.2)\fad(420,500)\be15}島津兵庫頭義弘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:14.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你說啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:19.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要一起回去薩摩的啊 豐久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:23.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:26.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算死也想死在薩摩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:31.07,Drifters Top,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,489)}島津中務少輔豐久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:30.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果伯父一個人能夠返回薩摩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:34.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我和士兵們都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:38.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這一戰 也是我們島津的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:46.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵們 準備射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現已為赴死之時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:59.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人是德川井伊的赤甲部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,作為對手來說並不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:05.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,赴死戰鬥的時刻正是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:10.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把那些傢伙活生生地放回薩州的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是德川井伊之恥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:13.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:20.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,來爭分奪秒吧 多一秒是一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:23.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把敵人拖延住 能留住一人是一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我等著你啊 豐久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:32.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我會在薩摩等著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:39.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我會等著你的 我不允許你死掉啊 豐久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個好伯父啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,豐久十分幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:49.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 就在這裡先廢掉第一隊騎兵的活動能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,裝彈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:53.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄準
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:55.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:04:59.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,別動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:00.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續衝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:17.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:21.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,島津中務少輔豐久 參上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,將死之兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:32.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,井伊兵部少輔直政 參上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:35.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們可是已經輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:47.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你的項上人頭歸作我的戰利品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:51.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說些什麼啊 你個死混球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:55.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,腦袋被砍的人不是我 而是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:02.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,保護直政大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:11.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:26.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:38.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是蠢蛋啊 井伊直政
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:45.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:50.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:51.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:52.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:53.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,直政大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:15.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:23.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等等啊 直政
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:26.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑啊 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,留下你的人頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:34.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,留下你的人頭啊 直政
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:03.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,回到薩摩去
