Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:52.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:07.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 什麼 這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:20.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是要回去的 回到薩摩去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:48.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？這裡是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:10.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「那是什麼」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「什麼 哥哥 死在路邊的人嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:24.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「這是怎麼回事 他居然渾身都是血」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:28.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「喂 你怎麼了 沒事吧？」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:33.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「沒事吧  你」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:36.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「哥哥 這個人是無耳的」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:44.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,見鬼了啊 果然到地獄了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:45.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「喂 你」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:48.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「不是單純的路人」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:51.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「根據他的言語 他應該是『漂流者』」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:56.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「唉？又是？怎麼辦啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:11:00.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「你要我說怎麼辦… 只好帶回去了吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:01.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「帶回廢城裡…」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:12.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「好重啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:20.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「實在太重了啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:23.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「如果不搬快點的話」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:28.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「如果給領主大人看到的話 事情就變得嚴重了」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:30.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「停下」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:34.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「如果再靠近這座城的話就殺了你們」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:38.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「敢回頭或者大聲呼喊也殺了你們」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「你們有何貴幹」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:48.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「你們的夥伴啊 這個人好像快要死的樣子」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「虧我們把他帶到這裡來了」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:54.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「說話再慢一點」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「我聽不清 還有聲音太小了」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:59.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「不放慢語速也殺了你」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:02.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「他和你們一樣都是漂流者對吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:04.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「你看 這裡」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:05.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「看」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:09.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「把他留在那裡」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:13.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「一如既往地不明所以」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:16.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「已經夠了 快走吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:21.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「不僅跑到森林來了」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:23.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「還遇見了漂流者 被發現了肯定會被殺死的」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:25.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「得趕快回去」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,武士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:35.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:40.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有村民抬了個人過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:42.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知是哪一位大名旗下的武士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:46.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:49.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已經奄奄一息了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:52.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:56.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒什麼像樣的藥還是給他處理一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:59.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,命硬運氣好的話或許還能活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:07.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:12.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這個塵世實在是太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:18.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,豐久 豐久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:21.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,初次上戰場就能砍下敵將腦袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:24.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 了不起的青年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:25.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:26.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,豐久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:31.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,父親 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:33.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是命大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:38.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口剛剛才縫好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便亂動可是會死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:45.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰 你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,誰？ 我才要問你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:52.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:55.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪裡來的什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,木瓜紋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:00.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是織田的家臣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,家臣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你說話注意點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:07.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是織田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,織田就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:17.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是織田前右府信長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:17.88,Drifters Top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(420,0)\pos(504,458.4)}織田前右府信長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:22.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:28.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你說你是信長？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:31.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信長公在很久以前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:35.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然這裡就是陰間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:40.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而你就是自稱信長的陰間小鬼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:47.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,極好極好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:03.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快來 拔毛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:10.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你要幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:13.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拔毛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:19.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:28.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你說了信長已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:32.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然世人都覺得我已經死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:34.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:38.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在京都本能寺裡遭到明智的背叛而被殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:41.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這已經是十八年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:42.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:46.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你說十八年前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:48.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那禿子入侵本能寺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:53.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還有我被丟到這個世界都只是半年前不到的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:56.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:16:00.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就是陰間的小鬼或者亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:03.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的話 實在是太荒謬了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:17.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,才十年十五年就在大吵大鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,從頭到尾實在是太好笑太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:23.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:27.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就告訴他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是與一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那須資隆与一正是在下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:34.60,Drifters Top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\pos(554.4,504)}那須資隆与一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是源平合戰時的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:41.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都四百年前的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:44.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會信你這大話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:48.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你說這是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:52.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:55.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定是在做夢 肯定是在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:57.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:00.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你又是哪裡來的什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:02.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,島津
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:04.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,島津豐久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:07.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,島津家久之子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:08.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,島津
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:10.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:15.89,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,{\frz339.3\pos(453.6,951.9)}島津
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:16.27,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,{\move(453.6,947.1,974.4,719.1,24,370)}{\frz339.3\pos(453.6,951.9)}島津
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:22.28,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,{\frz340.8\pos(974.4,719.1)}島津
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:15.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡 哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:22.28,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,{\frz343.2\pos(1291.2,697.5)}這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,九州島的最邊邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:20.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很偏遠的鄉下地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:25.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,島津大人的話我也認識
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:27.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的那個時代已經存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:31.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是在九州島的最偏遠地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:35.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,每一代都是鄉下人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要殺了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,活動得太激烈的話會丟掉性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:42.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那是剛剛才縫好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你的命真硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:46.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你說你是信長對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:54.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是死在本能寺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:56.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:18:00.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會被那個禿子殺死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:03.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,邊想著要逃出那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:06.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,邊帶著森蘭丸在本能寺內找出口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:09.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會死在這裡啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊都已經習慣被別人背叛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:16.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就出現在一個奇怪的「地方」了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,用些奇怪的石頭做成的過道上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:22.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,牆邊鑲嵌著無數的門在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:25.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個奇怪的男人就出現在那條通道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:27.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:33.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:35.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也見過那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:38.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也遇見過那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:42.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在關原合戰的撤退路上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:44.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,關原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,美濃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:47.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:49.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,德川軍與石田軍之間的大戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:53.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,石田不是那個端茶的小子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會和德川在那裡開戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:18:59.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你還說為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:02.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在關白死後天下又變回戰國時期了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:03.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你說關白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:06.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼關白可以奪得天下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:09.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為關白大人他一統了天下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,關白秀吉公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:16.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那只禿頭老鼠可以奪得天下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 好煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.98,0:19:22.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明智死了 柴田也死了 秀吉他就
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:24.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奪得了天下了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:27.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,勝家死了嗎 阿市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:28.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}兄長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:28.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丹羽呢 一益呢 利家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:33.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:35.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,織田家族現在只是幫家康端茶遞水的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:38.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,天下布武什麼的已經沒人記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:39.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:44.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信忠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:47.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我的兒子 他怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:50.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:53.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,二條城受到了光秀的進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:55.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他認為你已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:57.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就死守在二條城裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,直至到他戰死為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:05.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我愚蠢的兒子啊
